name: Early style painting
description:
某人跟我说底模女孩太多，于是找了PASTELBOY合并，去掉DARKSUSHI.

Someone told me there were too many girls in the bottom model, so they merged with PASTELBOY and removed DARKSUSHI.

20230614----------------------------------------------------------

懒得说些什么，早期风格的goodhand<2.5D，错指低于25%，你不需要badhandv5 badhand neg，bhand neg等等，它们只会造成乱肢体和多手指。

lazy to say something, earlystyle-goodhand<2.5D,Wrong finger lower than 25%, u don't need badhandv5 badhand-neg, bhand-neg and so on, They only cause messy limbs and multiple fingers..

20230603sliptline

超不喜欢目前的日漫风格，国漫也不喜欢，相比之下早期日漫还凑合，所以合成一种早期漫画风格，尽量远离写实和2.5D，试图与ANIME FINAL融合，后者简直了...

所以a+b搭配如下：

Darksoul:0.5

Nightsky:0.5

oldfish:0.75

chinese weding:0,5

This model<2.5D,hope so.
